thread.title: Kris
thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Kris

author: Kris
title: Kris
text: Dr. Danieitz is the best!! He is always friendly and thorough during our dogs annual visits. Over the years our dogs have had a few issues and each time he was able to quickly access and care for them. He is compassionate about his job and knowledgeable. I highly recommend OCVH!
